<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Terma Coffee — Single Origin. Pure Craft.</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    :root {
      --bg: #0d0b08;
      --bg2: #141108;
      --card: #181410;
      --cream: #f5f0e8;
      --gold: #c8a96e;
      --gold2: #a07840;
      --text: #e8e2d8;
      --muted: #7a7168;
      --border: #2a2420;
      --border2: #3a3028;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* GRAIN OVERLAY */
    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 512 512' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.75' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.035'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 9999;
    }

    /* ─── NAV ─── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 500;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 5%;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.1);
      background: rgba(13,11,8,0.9);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      transition: padding 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .nav-logo .brand {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--cream);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-logo .tagline {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      color: var(--gold);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    nav ul a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    nav ul a:hover { color: var(--cream); }

    .nav-cta {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold) !important;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.4rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: all 0.3s !important;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-cta:hover {
      background: var(--gold) !important;
      color: var(--bg) !important;
    }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8rem 5% 5rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 70% at 80% 50%, rgba(200,169,110,0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-left { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    .eyebrow {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both;
    }

    .eyebrow-line { width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }

    .eyebrow span {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 6vw, 5.5rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.1s ease both;
    }

    .hero h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.2s ease both;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      align-items: center;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.3s ease both;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--bg);
      border: none;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 2px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--cream);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      border: none;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--cream); }

    .btn-ghost::after {
      content: '→';
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-ghost:hover::after { transform: translateX(4px); }

    /* HERO RIGHT — visual */
    .hero-right {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s 0.4s ease both;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      width: 420px;
      height: 520px;
    }

    .hero-frame {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2);
      border-radius: 4px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-frame-inner {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1a140c 0%, #0d0b08 50%, #1e160c 100%);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* SVG coffee art in hero */
    .coffee-svg {
      width: 260px;
      height: 260px;
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -20px;
      left: -30px;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--bg);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
      text-align: center;
      min-width: 120px;
    }

    .hero-badge .num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-badge .label {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-top: 4px;
      display: block;
    }

    .corner-accent {
      position: absolute;
      top: -12px;
      right: -12px;
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-top: 2px solid var(--gold);
      border-right: 2px solid var(--gold);
    }

    /* ─── STRIP ─── */
    .strip {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem 5%;
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .strip-item {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 2rem;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .strip-item:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .strip-item .s-label {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .strip-item .s-val {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    /* ─── SECTION BASE ─── */
    section {
      padding: 8rem 5%;
      position: relative;
    }

    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 5rem;
    }

    .section-header .eyebrow {
      animation: none;
    }

    .section-header h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4vw, 3.8rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .section-header h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

    /* ─── PRODUCTS ─── */
    #products { background: var(--bg); }

    .products-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .product-card {
      background: var(--bg);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background 0.3s;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .product-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--gold);
      transform: scaleX(0);
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
      transform-origin: left;
    }

    .product-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }
    .product-card:hover { background: var(--card); }

    .product-category {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    /* Product icon art */
    .product-art {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .product-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.7rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--cream);
    }

    .product-card .origin {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .product-card .desc {
      font-size: 0.83rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .product-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }

    .price-block .price-label {
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .price-block .price {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .price-block .per {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }

    .add-btn {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border2);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .add-btn:hover {
      border-color: var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
      background: rgba(200,169,110,0.05);
    }

    /* Featured product */
    .product-card.featured {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2);
      grid-row: span 1;
    }

    .featured-badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 2.5rem;
      right: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 0.58rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.4);
      padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;
    }

    /* ─── PROCESS ─── */
    #process {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .process-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
    }

    .process-step {
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
      position: relative;
    }

    .process-step:last-child { border-right: none; }

    .step-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(200,169,110,0.12);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .step-icon {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .process-step h4 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .process-step p {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    /* ─── FOUNDER ─── */
    #founder {
      background: var(--bg);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8rem;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8rem 5%;
    }

    .founder-visual {
      position: relative;
    }

    .founder-frame {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .founder-frame::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(200,169,110,0.05) 0%, transparent 50%);
    }

    .founder-monogram {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 8rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(200,169,110,0.15);
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .founder-name-tag {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(13,11,8,0.95) 0%, transparent 100%);
    }

    .founder-name-tag .fn {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--cream);
      display: block;
    }

    .founder-name-tag .ft {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-top: 4px;
      display: block;
    }

    .founder-content .eyebrow { animation: none; }

    .founder-content h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .founder-content h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

    .founder-quote {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      border-left: 2px solid var(--gold);
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .founder-content p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    /* ─── TESTIMONIALS ─── */
    #reviews {
      background: var(--bg2);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .reviews-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .review-card {
      background: var(--bg2);
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
    }

    .stars {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .star {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .review-text {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .reviewer {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .reviewer-avatar {
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(200,169,110,0.15);
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.3);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .reviewer-name {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--cream);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .reviewer-loc {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* ─── CTA BANNER ─── */
    .cta-banner {
      padding: 8rem 5%;
      background: var(--bg);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .cta-banner h2 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 4.5vw, 4rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .cta-banner h2 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold); }

    .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 1.2rem; align-items: center; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 4rem 5%;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }

    .footer-brand .fb-logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cream);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .footer-brand .fb-tag {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-brand p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 260px;
    }

    .footer-col h5 {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }

    .footer-col ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer-col ul a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .footer-col ul a:hover { color: var(--cream); }

    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 1.5rem 5%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-bottom p {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .footer-bottom .gold { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes spin {
      to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ─── HAMBURGER ─── */
    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 4px;
      background: none;
      border: none;
    }
    .hamburger span {
      display: block;
      width: 24px;
      height: 1.5px;
      background: var(--cream);
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(1) { transform: translateY(6.5px) rotate(45deg); }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(2) { opacity: 0; }
    .hamburger.open span:nth-child(3) { transform: translateY(-6.5px) rotate(-45deg); }

    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      top: 68px; left: 0; right: 0;
      background: rgba(13,11,8,0.98);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      z-index: 499;
      padding: 2rem 5%;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .mobile-menu.open { display: flex; }
    .mobile-menu a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1.1rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .mobile-menu a:hover { color: var(--cream); }
    .mobile-menu .mob-cta {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--bg);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 2px;
      font-weight: 500;
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    /* ─── MOBILE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 1.1rem 5%; }
      nav ul { display: none; }
      .hamburger { display: flex; }

      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 7rem 5% 4rem; gap: 2rem; }
      .hero-right { display: none; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 10vw, 4rem); }
      .hero-sub { font-size: 0.85rem; }
      .btn-row, .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.8rem; }

      .strip { flex-direction: column; padding: 2rem 5%; }
      .strip-item { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem 0; text-align: left; }
      .strip-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

      section { padding: 5rem 5%; }
      .section-header { margin-bottom: 3rem; }
      .section-header h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 2.8rem); }

      .products-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .product-card { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }

      .process-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .process-step { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 2.5rem 0; }
      .process-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

      #founder > div { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; padding: 5rem 5% !important; gap: 3rem !important; }
      .founder-frame { aspect-ratio: 4/3; }
      .founder-monogram { font-size: 5rem; }
      .founder-content h2 { font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 7vw, 2.5rem); }

      .reviews-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }

      .cta-banner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 5rem 5%; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .cta-banner h2 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 3rem); }
      .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }

      footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; padding: 4rem 5%; }
      .footer-brand { grid-column: 1 / -1; }

      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; text-align: center; padding: 1.5rem 5%; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.6rem; }
      footer { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .products-grid { gap: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ─── NAV ─── -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <span class="brand">Terma Coffee</span>
      <span class="tagline">Single Origin. Pure Craft.</span>
    </div>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#products">Products</a></li>
      <li><a href="#process">Our Process</a></li>
      <li><a href="#founder">Our Story</a></li>
      <li><a href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
      <li><a href="#products" class="nav-cta">Shop Now</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Menu">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </nav>

  <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
    <a href="#products" onclick="closeMob()">Products</a>
    <a href="#process" onclick="closeMob()">Our Process</a>
    <a href="#founder" onclick="closeMob()">Our Story</a>
    <a href="#reviews" onclick="closeMob()">Reviews</a>
    <a href="#products" class="mob-cta" onclick="closeMob()">Shop Now</a>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── HERO ─── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span>Terma Coffee — Est. 2023</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Coffee at its<br/><em>finest form.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        From high-altitude farms to your cup — we source, roast, and deliver 
        exceptional single-origin coffees and artisan blends with uncompromising care.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="#products" class="btn-primary">Shop Collection</a>
        <a href="#founder" class="btn-ghost">Our Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="hero-frame">
          <div class="hero-frame-inner">
            <!-- Elegant coffee cup SVG art -->
            <svg class="coffee-svg" viewBox="0 0 260 260" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <!-- Steam -->
              <path d="M100 60 Q105 48 100 36" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none">
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0;1;0" dur="2.5s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
              </path>
              <path d="M130 52 Q135 38 130 24" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none">
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0;1;0" dur="2.5s" begin="0.5s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
              </path>
              <path d="M160 60 Q165 48 160 36" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none">
                <animate attributeName="opacity" values="0;1;0" dur="2.5s" begin="1s" repeatCount="indefinite"/>
              </path>
              <!-- Cup body -->
              <path d="M72 90 L80 180 Q80 192 92 192 L168 192 Q180 192 180 180 L188 90 Z" fill="rgba(30,22,14,0.9)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <!-- Coffee surface -->
              <ellipse cx="130" cy="90" rx="58" ry="10" fill="rgba(120,80,40,0.8)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <!-- Latte art -->
              <ellipse cx="130" cy="90" rx="30" ry="5" fill="rgba(200,150,90,0.25)"/>
              <path d="M115 88 Q130 82 145 88 Q130 94 115 88Z" fill="rgba(240,200,140,0.15)"/>
              <!-- Saucer -->
              <ellipse cx="130" cy="198" rx="74" ry="10" fill="rgba(30,22,14,0.7)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.35)" stroke-width="1"/>
              <ellipse cx="130" cy="197" rx="64" ry="7" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.15)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
              <!-- Handle -->
              <path d="M188 120 Q220 120 220 150 Q220 178 188 175" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.5)" stroke-width="2" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              <!-- Brand text -->
              <text x="130" y="145" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Cormorant Garamond', serif" font-size="11" fill="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" letter-spacing="3">TERMA</text>
              <!-- Corner decorations -->
              <rect x="30" y="30" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.15)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
              <rect x="210" y="210" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.15)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
              <!-- Beans decoration -->
              <ellipse cx="50" cy="180" rx="6" ry="9" fill="rgba(120,70,30,0.4)" transform="rotate(-30 50 180)"/>
              <line x1="47" y1="172" x2="53" y2="188" stroke="rgba(90,50,20,0.5)" stroke-width="0.7"/>
              <ellipse cx="210" cy="90" rx="6" ry="9" fill="rgba(120,70,30,0.4)" transform="rotate(20 210 90)"/>
              <line x1="207" y1="82" x2="213" y2="98" stroke="rgba(90,50,20,0.5)" stroke-width="0.7"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="num">8+</span>
          <span class="label">Origins</span>
        </div>
        <div class="corner-accent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── STRIP ─── -->
  <div class="strip">
    <div class="strip-item">
      <div class="s-label">Sourced from</div>
      <div class="s-val">Ethiopia · Colombia · Nepal</div>
    </div>
    <div class="strip-item">
      <div class="s-label">Roast Profile</div>
      <div class="s-val">Light · Medium · Dark</div>
    </div>
    <div class="strip-item">
      <div class="s-label">Free Shipping</div>
      <div class="s-val">Orders above NPR 2,000</div>
    </div>
    <div class="strip-item">
      <div class="s-label">Freshness</div>
      <div class="s-val">Roasted to Order</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── PRODUCTS ─── -->
  <section id="products">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span>The Collection</span>
      </div>
      <h2>Crafted for the<br/><em>discerning cup.</em></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="products-grid">

      <!-- Product 1 -->
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-category">Whole Bean</div>
        <svg class="product-art" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none">
          <ellipse cx="40" cy="40" rx="18" ry="26" fill="rgba(120,70,30,0.3)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.5)" stroke-width="1" transform="rotate(-20 40 40)"/>
          <line x1="32" y1="24" x2="48" y2="56" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(-20 40 40)"/>
          <ellipse cx="56" cy="35" rx="12" ry="18" fill="rgba(100,55,20,0.3)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.35)" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(15 56 35)"/>
          <line x1="50" y1="21" x2="62" y2="49" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="0.7" transform="rotate(15 56 35)"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Ethiopian Yirgacheffe</h3>
        <div class="origin">Ethiopia · Light Roast · Washed</div>
        <p class="desc">Bright and floral with notes of jasmine, bergamot, and a lemon citrus finish. A classic of the craft.</p>
        <div class="product-footer">
          <div class="price-block">
            <div class="price-label">Price</div>
            <div class="price">NPR 1,450</div>
            <div class="per">per 250g</div>
          </div>
          <button class="add-btn">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 2 — Featured -->
      <div class="product-card featured reveal">
        <div class="featured-badge">Best Seller</div>
        <div class="product-category">Whole Bean</div>
        <svg class="product-art" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none">
          <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="22" fill="rgba(80,45,15,0.3)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="14" fill="rgba(100,60,20,0.2)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.25)" stroke-width="0.7"/>
          <circle cx="40" cy="40" r="6" fill="rgba(200,169,110,0.15)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.5)" stroke-width="0.7"/>
          <line x1="40" y1="18" x2="40" y2="62" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          <line x1="18" y1="40" x2="62" y2="40" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Colombian Huila</h3>
        <div class="origin">Colombia · Medium Roast · Natural</div>
        <p class="desc">Rich chocolate and caramel sweetness balanced with red fruit acidity. Smooth, full-bodied, and deeply satisfying.</p>
        <div class="product-footer">
          <div class="price-block">
            <div class="price-label">Price</div>
            <div class="price">NPR 1,650</div>
            <div class="per">per 250g</div>
          </div>
          <button class="add-btn">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 3 -->
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-category">Whole Bean</div>
        <svg class="product-art" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none">
          <path d="M20 55 L40 20 L60 55 Z" fill="rgba(80,40,10,0.3)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M28 55 L40 33 L52 55 Z" fill="rgba(200,169,110,0.08)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.2)" stroke-width="0.6" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Nepalese Highland</h3>
        <div class="origin">Nepal · Medium-Dark · Honey</div>
        <p class="desc">A rare Himalayan origin. Earthy and complex with hints of dark fruit, cedar, and a lingering sweetness.</p>
        <div class="product-footer">
          <div class="price-block">
            <div class="price-label">Price</div>
            <div class="price">NPR 1,800</div>
            <div class="per">per 250g</div>
          </div>
          <button class="add-btn">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 4 -->
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-category">Ground Powder</div>
        <svg class="product-art" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none">
          <rect x="22" y="30" width="36" height="28" rx="3" fill="rgba(80,45,15,0.3)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="30" y="22" width="20" height="10" rx="2" fill="rgba(100,60,20,0.4)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.35)" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <line x1="28" y1="40" x2="52" y2="40" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          <line x1="28" y1="46" x2="52" y2="46" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          <line x1="28" y1="52" x2="52" y2="52" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.2)" stroke-width="0.5"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Morning Blend Powder</h3>
        <div class="origin">Multi-Origin · Medium · Fine Grind</div>
        <p class="desc">Precision-ground for drip, French press, or Moka pot. Consistent, vibrant, and ready to brew.</p>
        <div class="product-footer">
          <div class="price-block">
            <div class="price-label">Price</div>
            <div class="price">NPR 1,100</div>
            <div class="per">per 250g</div>
          </div>
          <button class="add-btn">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 5 -->
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-category">Ground Powder</div>
        <svg class="product-art" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none">
          <ellipse cx="40" cy="50" rx="22" ry="10" fill="rgba(80,45,15,0.25)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="0.8"/>
          <rect x="28" y="28" width="24" height="22" rx="2" fill="rgba(80,45,15,0.35)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <path d="M34 28 L34 22 L46 22 L46 28" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Espresso Dark Powder</h3>
        <div class="origin">Brazil·Ethiopia · Dark · Ultra-Fine</div>
        <p class="desc">Bold, intense, and unforgiving. Engineered for espresso machines demanding the very best from every shot.</p>
        <div class="product-footer">
          <div class="price-block">
            <div class="price-label">Price</div>
            <div class="price">NPR 1,350</div>
            <div class="per">per 250g</div>
          </div>
          <button class="add-btn">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Product 6 -->
      <div class="product-card reveal">
        <div class="product-category">Coffee Beans</div>
        <svg class="product-art" viewBox="0 0 80 80" fill="none">
          <ellipse cx="30" cy="45" rx="10" ry="15" fill="rgba(100,55,20,0.35)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.4)" stroke-width="1" transform="rotate(-15 30 45)"/>
          <line x1="24" y1="32" x2="36" y2="58" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.35)" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(-15 30 45)"/>
          <ellipse cx="50" cy="38" rx="10" ry="15" fill="rgba(80,40,10,0.35)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.35)" stroke-width="1" transform="rotate(10 50 38)"/>
          <line x1="44" y1="25" x2="56" y2="51" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(10 50 38)"/>
          <ellipse cx="40" cy="55" rx="8" ry="12" fill="rgba(90,50,15,0.3)" stroke="rgba(200,169,110,0.3)" stroke-width="0.8" transform="rotate(5 40 55)"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Terma Signature Blend</h3>
        <div class="origin">3-Origin · Medium · Whole Bean</div>
        <p class="desc">Our house blend — a carefully calibrated harmony of three origins creating our most balanced and beloved cup.</p>
        <div class="product-footer">
          <div class="price-block">
            <div class="price-label">Price</div>
            <div class="price">NPR 1,550</div>
            <div class="per">per 250g</div>
          </div>
          <button class="add-btn">+</button>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── PROCESS ─── -->
  <section id="process">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span>How We Work</span>
      </div>
      <h2>From seed to<br/><em>your cup.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid">
      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h4>Direct Sourcing</h4>
        <p>We build direct relationships with small-lot farmers across Ethiopia, Colombia, and the Himalayas — ensuring fair pricing and traceable origins.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h4>Sample Roasting</h4>
        <p>Every new lot is sample-roasted and cupped by our team before a single bag is ordered. Only the highest scoring lots make the cut.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h4>Precision Roasting</h4>
        <p>We roast in small batches on a drum roaster, dialing each origin to its ideal profile — preserving what makes each coffee unique.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step reveal">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <h4>Freshness Delivered</h4>
        <p>Orders are roasted within 48 hours of dispatch and shipped in nitrogen-flushed, valve-sealed bags to lock in peak freshness.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── FOUNDER ─── -->
  <section id="founder" style="padding:0">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;align-items:center;gap:8rem;padding:8rem 5%">
      <div class="founder-visual reveal">
        <div class="founder-frame">
          <div class="founder-monogram">SG</div>
          <div class="founder-name-tag">
            <span class="fn">Sagar</span>
            <span class="ft">Founder &amp; Head Roaster — Terma Coffee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="founder-content reveal">
        <div class="eyebrow">
          <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
          <span>The Founder</span>
        </div>
        <h2>Built on a<br/><em>love for the craft.</em></h2>
        <blockquote class="founder-quote">
          "I started Terma because I believed Nepal deserved access to world-class coffee — and that the world deserved to taste what grows in our own mountains."
        </blockquote>
        <p>Terma Coffee was born from a single conviction: that exceptional coffee should be honest, traceable, and beautiful in its simplicity. No shortcuts. No compromises.</p>
        <p>From sourcing trips to high-altitude farms to evenings behind the roaster, every bean that leaves our facility has been personally approved — because quality is not a claim, it's a practice.</p>
        <a href="#products" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:1rem;display:inline-block">Explore the Collection</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── REVIEWS ─── -->
  <section id="reviews" style="padding-bottom:6rem">
    <div class="section-header reveal" style="margin-bottom:0">
      <div class="eyebrow">
        <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
        <span>Reviews</span>
      </div>
      <h2>What our customers<br/><em>are saying.</em></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card reveal">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"The Ethiopian Yirgacheffe changed how I think about coffee. Floral, bright, and unlike anything I'd had before. Terma has a customer for life."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar">AR</div>
          <div>
            <div class="reviewer-name">Anish Rana</div>
            <div class="reviewer-loc">Kathmandu, Nepal</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card reveal">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"I've ordered from specialty roasters around the world. Terma's Colombian Huila sits right up there. The balance is extraordinary — chocolate and fruit in perfect tension."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar">PM</div>
          <div>
            <div class="reviewer-name">Priya Manandhar</div>
            <div class="reviewer-loc">Lalitpur, Nepal</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="review-card reveal">
        <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="review-text">"Fast shipping, beautiful packaging, and the Nepalese Highland is something truly special. Proud that this quality exists right here in Nepal."</p>
        <div class="reviewer">
          <div class="reviewer-avatar">SK</div>
          <div>
            <div class="reviewer-name">Suraj KC</div>
            <div class="reviewer-loc">Pokhara, Nepal</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ─── CTA ─── -->
  <div class="cta-banner">
    <h2>Ready to experience<br/><em>exceptional coffee?</em></h2>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="#products" class="btn-primary">Shop Now</a>
      <a href="#founder" class="btn-ghost">Our Story</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── FOOTER ─── -->
  <footer>
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <span class="fb-logo">Terma Coffee</span>
      <span class="fb-tag">Single Origin. Pure Craft.</span>
      <p>Sourcing and roasting exceptional coffee from around the world — delivered fresh to your door from Kathmandu.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h5>Shop</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Whole Beans</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Ground Powder</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Signature Blend</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Gift Sets</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Subscriptions</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h5>Company</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Our Story</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Sourcing</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Roasting</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Blog</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h5>Support</h5>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Shipping Info</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Returns</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
